'''''Timoth 4''''' was an [[CR92a Assassin-class corvette|CR92a ''Assassin''-class corvette]] belonging to the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothans]]. Timoth 4 was carrying specialized decoding computers which could decipher the [[Death Star II plans|secret data]] onboard the ''[[Suprosa]]'', a [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] freighter that was stolen by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]]. [[Tan (title)|Tan]] [[Maarek Stele/Legends|Maarek Stele]] inspected this corvette under orders of the secret order before allowing the ship to enter hyperspace.

==Behind the scenes==
According to ''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance]]'', the plans were delivered to a corvette named [[Razor (CR90 corvette)|''Razor'']].

